The required parameters for a Django project for each test are as follows:

* For the "Read Product Overview" function on the Home page, the URL parameter value is '/', which represents the homepage of the Django project.
* For the "List Key Features" function on the Features page, the link_id parameter value is the component ID for redirecting to the features page in the homepage, and the features_list_id parameter value is the component ID of the key features list.
* For the "View Pricing Plans" function on the Pricing page, the link_id parameter value is the component ID for redirecting to the pricing page from the homepage, and the pricing_table_id parameter value is the component ID of the pricing table.
* For the "Contact Sales" function in the Pricing page, the contact_form_id parameter value is the component ID of the contact form, name_input_name parameter value is the name attribute of the name input field, email_input_name parameter value is the name attribute of the email input field, submit_button_id parameter value is the component ID of submitting the form, and message_input_name parameter value is the name attribute of the message input field.
* For the "Contact Sales Back" function in the Pricing page, the back_id parameter value is the component ID of hyperlink that links to the last page.
* For the "Pricing Back Home" function on the Pricing page, the back_home_id parameter value is the component ID of hyperlink that link to the homepage.
* For the "Company Background" function in the About Us page, the link_id parameter value is the component ID for redirecting to the background page in the homepage, and the background_section_id parameter value is the component ID of the company background section.
* For the "About Back Home" function in the About Us page, the back_home_id parameter value is the component ID of hyperlink that link to the homepage.
* For the "FAQ" function on the Support page, the faq_section_id parameter value is the component ID of the FAQ section.
* For the "Support Message" function in the Support page, the contact_form_id parameter value is the component ID of the contact form, name_input_name parameter value is the name attribute of the name input field, email_input_name parameter value is the name attribute of the email input field, submit_button_id parameter value is the component ID of submitting the form, and issue_input_name parameter value is the name attribute of the issue input field.
* For the "Support Back Home" function in the Support page, the back_home_id parameter value is the component ID of hyperlink that link to the homepage.
